{"tid":460230,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"關於巴士超載一問","createTime":"2017-11-06T12:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T18:41:50.000Z","uid":34983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b8400ba5c09d4c1c517637169e6d05ab61f8663c","tid":460230,"uid":34983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:49:47.000Z","msg":"成日繁忙時間都見到巴士超載<br />\n即係下層企滿咗個限額<br />\n<br />\n今日係到諗 <br />\n咁多年都好似無人執過法(?)<br />\n究竟如果有日咁唔好彩超載出事<br />\n<br />\n法律上係犯咗法(?)<br />\n如果有人死 司機比人告 會告咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n司機應該負全責定係公司？<br />\n公司好似又無人同司機溝通過<br />\n而保險又有無得賠？<br />\n到最後傷者會唔會無錢賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n我明白繁忙時間無車無位真係好戇鳩<br />\n有人會諗有得上唔上咩屌<br />\n有時司機仲叫人行入啲 到站仲比人上<br />\n好易好心做壞事<br />\n<br />\n係YouTube搵到一段98年嘅片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1ybw92KRThw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1ybw92KRThw&d=AzlJ5qUn41umfvhC4ygFVtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=e3ada9eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1ybw92KRThw</a>"},{"pid":"1d933fc769ec38151788744062d0802abc3de6e6","tid":460230,"uid":34983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9efb8a81c3839e49629b2d8dd48e93a39547d6c7","tid":460230,"uid":100406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:14:45.000Z","msg":"一架正常車企37人<br />\n迫到沙甸魚咁都好難超載喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲而家企到70人添<br />\n你唔諗下地鐵繁時架架客量130%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d061adbe61e065a6a41e9c2f60a97754275da757","tid":460230,"uid":8033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:20:05.000Z","msg":"下層企位47人<br />\n邊企到咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed02f778fad042f1b807772977e26bb57a3019e","tid":460230,"uid":34983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下層企位47人<br />\n邊企到咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最大架先47？<br />\n今日親身數過 未過出口有至少30人<br />\n仲有人企樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0270264f71d1ba4f7efdfb8781c5c6d748a979ec","tid":460230,"uid":34983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d282f1129b62b0e56c45522bc95c33000abd95c","tid":460230,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"除咗兩軸雙層限企20人比較有可以爆quota<br />\n其他車起碼限企去到30人 去到69人都有<br />\n總之係唔會有可能企到咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2fa40777c29b7626a70f67f0eece13c63c05d0e","tid":460230,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T17:22:11.000Z","msg":"其實巴士佬個日心情好的話。<br />\n企到黃線就可以唔俾人上。直接飛站。"},{"pid":"1735129354bd4ca5fe3f49724110f8475a4e79ab","tid":460230,"uid":34983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除咗兩軸雙層限企20人比較有可以爆quota<br />\n其他車起碼限企去到30人 去到69人都有<br />\n總之係唔會有可能企到咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有(條例 定？)寫 不准過黃線<br />\n咁係法例規定 定 其實係虛設<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似mtr咁？"},{"pid":"fcf9007a9533998d0acbb6e997ea7e47e2d087b4","tid":460230,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T18:41:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除咗兩軸雙層限企20人比較有可以爆quota<br />\n其他車起碼限企去到30人 去到69人都有<br />\n總之係唔會有可能企到咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有(條例 定？)寫 不准過黃線<br />\n咁係法例規定 定 其實係虛設<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似mtr咁？</blockquote><br />\n香港法例第230A章《公共巴士服務規例》<br />\n13A 乘客及擬成為乘客的人的一般行為<br />\n(3) 通道上可劃一橫線，以顯示乘客在巴士移動時不可站立的地方。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.blis.gov.hk/blis_pdf.nsf/CurAllChinDoc/E228696C4AE549C5482575EE00502BBE/$FILE/CAP_230A_c_b5.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.blis.gov.hk%2Fblis_pdf.nsf%2FCurAllChinDoc%2FE228696C4AE549C5482575EE00502BBE%2F%24FILE%2FCAP_230A_c_b5.pdf&d=AzlJ5qUn41umfvhC4ygFVtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d2e83014\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.blis.gov.hk/blis_pdf.nsf/CurAllChinDoc/E228696C4AE549C5482575EE00502BBE/$FILE/CAP_230A_c_b5.pdf</a>"}]}